'''Conflict-Orange''' was a stage of [[New Republic Defense Force/Legends|New Republic Defense Force]] military status.

It was raised only when combat was imminent, for example, when an enemy force had been detected nearby but New Republic forces had not yet been detected by the their perspective foes. Other stages of military status included [[Conflict-Red]] and [[Conflict-Yellow]].

